<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天下午，师徒四人在一个小溪边休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在吃桃子和野草莓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们肯定离西天越来越近了。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们走了好几年了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们好像走了几千年了。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还需要走很远的路呢。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，别担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们最终会到达西天，登上灵山的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如来佛祖就在那儿的雷音寺里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧咬了一口桃子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雷音寺一定很美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雷音寺非常壮观。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里金光闪闪的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒抱怨道：“也就是说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们到了西天，还得爬上山去？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>光是想想，就让我觉得累。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真希望取经快点儿结束。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒点了点头。“你也觉得走累了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”悟净表情严肃地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是听你抱怨听累了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都安静了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，悟净微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，大家都大笑起来，八戒也笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真有意思，悟净。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧站起来说：“我们该走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在天黑之前，我想找找村子或寺院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个小时后，他们走在山路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>路弯弯曲曲的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前面出现一个小寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧大吃一惊。“那里就是雷音寺吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许吧。”八戒说，“那里金光闪闪的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它在山上。”悟净补充了一句。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“那不是雷音寺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们还没到西天呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空仔细地看了看寺院，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得小心！寺院上面有黑云。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人继续走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们就来到了寺院门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门上的牌匾上写着“小雷音寺”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里一定是佛祖的寺院！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是佛祖的寺院。我们继续走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。”八戒说，“这个寺院金光闪闪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定是个重要的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的。”悟空说，“我们真的......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要进去。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是佛教寺院。我们得进去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧打开寺院的门，走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净跟了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气，跟着他们走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里肯定有问题。悟空拿出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人走进寺院的正殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>正前方有一个巨大的金佛像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看见那个佛像了吗，悟空？”唐僧问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是真的佛教寺院。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，有人大喊道：“谁竟敢不拜佛祖就进来了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧吓得发抖。他马上跪下拜佛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净也拜了佛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空继续站着，仔细地看着佛像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛像看起来非常可疑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么不拜？”那个声音问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧小声说，“你讲点礼貌！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不拜你！”悟空大喊，“你其实......”当啷啷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的喊声还没结束，两个金铙就从上面掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金铙紧紧地合在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空被关在了里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！”唐僧喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，佛像变成了妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他长着两条黄眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个妖怪站起来笑着喊道：“唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>